com.ekito.simpleKML.model

Class SchemaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ekito.simpleKML.model.SchemaData

  • public class SchemaData
extends java.lang.Object
    This element is used in conjunction with Schema to add typed custom data to a KML Feature. The Schema element (identified by the schemaUrl attribute) declares the custom data type. The actual data objects ("instances" of the custom data) are defined using the SchemaData element. The schemaURL can be a full URL, a reference to a Schema ID defined in an external KML file, or a reference to a Schema ID defined in the same KML file.
